    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD model meets the required credibility factors for MRL 2 at High assurance. All 7 assessed factors meet or exceed required levels. Pressure-head and hemolysis validation at operating point 1 demonstrate adequate model fidelity. The team notes that formal comparator dataset registration for operating points 2, 3, and 4 was deferred pending data management system migration; the team judged this administrative gap acceptable given the consistency of results across operating points and the conservative RH < 1 acceptance criterion met at all points. The High assurance declaration reflects the elevated regulatory context of the 510(k) submission.",
